-- RIM surges on China BlackBerry pact
-- 
-- Tue Oct 23, 2007 2:33pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/23/us-markets-stocks-rim-idUSN2327539520071023

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of BlackBerry maker Research in Motion Ltd RIM.TORIMM.O jumped more than 6 percent to a record $121.10 on Tuesday after the company announced it had entered a deal to distribute its BlackBerry smartphones in China with Alcatel-Lucent ( ALU.N ). 

